to the editor your april 8 business day article about penthouse magazine quotes me as saying there is no future for adult business in mass market magazines and you report that i acknowledge that the run of penthouse magazine is at an end what i meant was that the future growth of the industry lies in the electronic sphere a cursory glance at the statistics would show that the adult magazine field remains healthy penthouse has no intention of ceasing publication penthouse remains one of the best recognized brand names in the world and we are confident in our business and its long term viability bob guccione editor in chief and publisher general media communications new york april 8 2002

